			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				If you have a chance ask around about routers from other EQ users. See if anyone had problems setting them up or good brands to use. I've been looking through some forums, but havn't found much info. Circuit City has a Microsoft Router for $40, which seems like a good price. It might, notice the word might, be easier to set up being a microsoft product. <br>  <br>  <br> anyone shed some light on this topic from personal experience? <br>  <br> as well as moving from 512DDR to 712DDR ram, it worth the jump? <br> 		

			</td>
